    "headline": "ArcWest Announces Results From 2025 Drilling of the Todd Creek Project",
    "summary": "Vancouver, British Columbia--(Newsfile Corp. - March 16, 2026) - ArcWest Exploration Inc. (TSXV: AWX) (\"ArcWest\") announces results from a drill program funded by Freeport-McMoRan Mineral Properties Canada Inc. (\"Freeport\"), as per the March 2023 Todd Creek Earn-In Agreement, on its wholly owned Todd Creek Copper (\"Cu\") - Gold (\"Au\") Project in British Columbia's Golden Triangle. ArcWest's 100% owned, 21,700-hectare Todd Creek Cu-Au project adjoins Newmont Corporation's Brucejack Gold Mine...",
